WEBVTT

00:00.231 --> 00:04.671
Here are some phrases you can use when interrupting someone in a conversation.

00:06.556 --> 00:08.177
Sorry to interrupt but...

00:09.861 --> 00:11.829
Sorry for the interruption but...

00:17.391 --> 00:18.943
I hate to interrupt but...

00:20.783 --> 00:21.909
Excuse me,...

00:23.655 --> 00:24.719
Excuse me, but...

00:26.469 --> 00:27.782
Can I add something here?

00:29.651 --> 00:31.489
I'm sorry to cut this short but...

00:33.412 --> 00:34.756
This will only take a minute.

00:36.628 --> 00:38.751
Excuse me, I'd like to say something.

00:40.636 --> 00:43.125
Sorry, could you explain that a little more?

